        {
            "title": "俄烏在美國牽頭下於日內瓦啟動第三輪會談 議題料包含領土等五條軌道",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 由美國牽頭、旨在結束俄烏戰爭的第三輪談判周二在日內瓦啟動，但外界對會談取得突破以實現停火止戰幾乎沒有抱太大的希望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">烏方代表團由烏克蘭國家安全與國防委員會秘書Rustem Umerov率領。他在Telegram發文宣布談判開始，並表示議題包括安全與人道問題。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">俄方代表團則由俄羅斯總統助理Vladimir Medinsky帶隊。談判計畫於周三繼續進行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國特使史蒂夫·威特科夫以及總統唐納德·川普的女婿賈裡德·庫什納此前曾出席前兩輪會談，目前也在日內瓦。兩人周二上午參加了與伊朗官員的另一場談判。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-aa2dab0f-2d09-3702-9404-293e3b34e087-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據國際文傳電訊引述克里姆林宮發言人Dmitry Peskov周一的話稱，本輪談判議題將比此前兩輪在阿布達比的會談更為廣泛。阿布達比會談討論了潛在停火所涉及的軍事參數，但在結束敵對行動方面未見明顯進展。另據塔斯社報導，日內瓦會談將包含五條軌道，包括領土、軍事、政治和經濟等議題。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Peskov還表示，俄方代表團還將包括軍事情報負責人Igor Kostyukov。他先前在阿聯酋談判中負責帶領俄羅斯代表團。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Russia and Ukraine Start Talks in Geneva With Expectations Low</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84%E7%83%8F%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%89%BD%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%BC%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A7%E7%93%A6%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E8%BC%AA%E6%9C%83%E8%AB%87-%E8%AD%B0%E9%A1%8C%E6%96%99%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E9%A0%98%E5%9C%9F%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%94%E6%A2%9D%E8%BB%8C%E9%81%93-134909580.html",
