        {
            "title": "美銀調查顯示AI泡沫成首要尾部風險 資本支出過熱擔憂創紀錄",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"610\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1WfBtTcf4KKBLFsabtQP4w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4868d2299b215780782e9fc5b6af1e3a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國銀行最新基金經理調查顯示，創紀錄數量的投資者認為企業支出過高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">策略師Michael Hartnett在報告中指出，儘管參與該項調查的投資者看漲情緒達到了2021年6月以來的最高水平，但約有35%的人警告稱企業正出現過度投資的情況，這是過去二十年來數據中所見的最高比例。他們同時也在減少對科技股的敞口。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年資本支出預計將創紀錄水平，美國四大科技公司合計2026年支出預計將達到約6500億美元。市場對這些預測反應不一：微軟股價遭遇近六年最大跌幅，因投資者擔憂投資回報周期過長，而Meta Platforms Inc.公佈雄心勃勃的人工智能支出計畫後股價飆升逾11%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-527cbb60-cb0f-312f-a935-3948a604e0d2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最新美銀調查顯示，四分之一受訪者認為「人工智能泡沫」是市場面臨的首要尾部風險，30%受訪者指出科技巨頭在人工智能領域的資本支出最有可能成為引發信貸危機的源頭。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"630\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RzhZMZJ8IULaA9ohQRf0rA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fa083bec91048d1706ece16a4c2ccbfd\" width=\"907\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:907px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hartnett表示，受訪者認為當前的資本支出「過熱」，儘管他們對全球企業盈利的前景持2021年8月以來最為樂觀的看法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hartnett在報告中指出，投資者正撤離科技股和美元，同時增加對能源、材料及必需消費品板塊的配置。科技股配置比例降幅創2025年3月以來之最，受訪者對該板塊的淨超配比例僅為5%，較一個月前的淨超配19%大幅回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">資金從美國股市轉向新興市場及歐洲市場的規模達到2021年2月以來最高水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"610\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C9w2U9U09W48oJ6UrI5KZg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c22ce13aec27fe13556b17674a542b27\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在其他領域，近期小型股的優異表現凸顯了市場正從科技巨頭轉向其他板塊。調查參與者對小型股相對於大型股的超配程度，達到自2021年4月以來的最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BofA Survey Shows Investor Worry Over Capex Race at Record High</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael Msika.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BAai%E6%B3%A1%E6%B2%AB%E6%88%90%E9%A6%96%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%BE%E9%83%A8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E9%81%8E%E7%86%B1%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-123910476.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-17 21:13:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國將向菲律賓部署更多尖端飛彈系統 或引發中國不滿",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國將向菲律賓部署更多飛彈系統。隨著兩國加強防務關係，此舉可能引起中國的不滿。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據兩國高級別官員周一在馬尼拉會晤後於周二發布的聯合聲明，美國和菲律賓致力於「繼續並推動增加在菲律賓部署美國的尖端飛彈和無人系統」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國在2024年向菲律賓部署了「堤豐」飛彈系統。該系統可發射多用途火箭彈，包括射程足以覆蓋中國大片地區的「戰斧」巡航飛彈。中國政府此前表示，這種武器可能破壞穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，美國去年在年度軍演期間，向菲律賓派遣了NMESIS反艦飛彈系統。演習包括在台灣附近的呂宋島北部以及巴丹群島舉行演練。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2f85d87e-e3a0-3848-90f6-76702dda93ff-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US to Deploy More Cutting-Edge Missile Systems to Philippines</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Cliff Harvey Venzon.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E5%90%91%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%96%E7%AB%AF%E9%A3%9B%E5%BD%88%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E6%88%96%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF-132824209.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-17 22:23:55",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐盟內部阻力升溫 對俄最新制裁方案或被削弱",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"764\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mwT4NQqRhwjSRS1sImL2cA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc2NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/69147d0b3891b4883d1c1e7c50352d12\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐盟試圖懲罰俄羅斯用於非法銷售石油的外國港口和銀行的提議正遭遇阻力，這可能削弱歐盟的最新一輪制裁方案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露，一些成員國就針對格魯吉亞和印度尼西亞港口的提議持謹慎態度。義大利和匈牙利尤其對格魯吉亞的Kulev港表示擔憂，而希臘和馬耳他對印尼一處港口表示猶豫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因討論未公開消息而要求匿名的這些知情人士表示，義大利和西班牙還對針對古巴一家銀行的擬議處罰提出異議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在此之前，希臘和馬耳他還對用禁止海事服務來取代對俄羅斯石油價格上限的相關提議表示擔憂。該舉措需獲得七國集團支持，美國尚未明確表態。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6a626c0e-882e-3845-bd00-0fd30a8ba25c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，日益增加的阻力可能會削弱歐盟的最新制裁方案。歐盟委員會本月早些時候公佈的這些提議旨在進一步抑制俄羅斯的石油收入，以施壓普丁結束對烏克蘭的戰爭。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"764\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Zp2rI6JPsCYsjGTkFLDJUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc2NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0d1e8e075f5d0d45bed0500f6d40ae0f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟各國特使周一討論了相關措施。歐盟希望在本月批准該制裁方案。制裁措施在通過前需獲得所有成員國支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">義大利拒絕就制裁談判置評。希臘發言人此前拒絕就海事服務禁令發表評論，周二也未立即回應置評請求。馬耳他駐布魯塞爾發言人上周表示，該國正在進行技術層面的討論，以確保最終方案具有可操作性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">匈牙利長期反對其認為會限制本國能源供應的措施。歐盟委員會和西班牙政府未立即回應置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：俄羅斯金屬面臨圍堵 歐盟新一輪制裁據悉擬納入銅和鉑</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題EU Countries’ Resistance Risks Blunting Latest Russia Sanctions</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Daniel Basteiro、Sotiris Nikas.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E9%98%BB%E5%8A%9B%E5%8D%87%E6%BA%AB-%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%84%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%88%96%E8%A2%AB%E5%89%8A%E5%BC%B1-132227041.html",
